{"tid":1788533,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣選舉已成定局 波特王事件再次助攻蔡英文！〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉","createTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T04:10:27.000Z","uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee66a674852232c3182175fd000e0c014b19c09a","tid":1788533,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IF5UrHtU-xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIF5UrHtU-xc&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6hyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=1db3a3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IF5UrHtU-xc</a>"},{"pid":"2f6a7cbabd8806172fb4d98e6659e1890de5da8e","tid":1788533,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/29/0Ze8sM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F29%2F0Ze8sM.png&h=34563f9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffdff41ae06a27484a895d198d5cf54b409052e5","tid":1788533,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"陷家產啦今次"},{"pid":"53890bd6645e5db7bcd27b0cfcc817c04620757d","tid":1788533,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稅局行動宣言：<br />\n<br />\n稅局，納稅人金錢吐納之處。六月以降，香港警隊搬出大量催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈甚或實彈，一一射向香港市民。購置武器，所費不菲，警隊資金何來？稅款必是一大來源。港人金錢，變作供養濫暴警隊的薪水，變作不人道武器還於港人之身，這絕非稅款的正當用途。政府無能，特首執拗難以平息民憤，何解需公帑埋單？<br />\n<br />\n香港市民安分守己，繳納血汗金錢；今民意所指為五大訴求，政府乃人民公僕，理應善用公帑以平眾怒，藉稅款促進訴求之達成以撫民心。然林鄭政府恣意調用港人金錢，屢行政治操作，維護腐敗議會，投稅款入朽壞警隊之血海，廣大市民如何甘心將夙夜辛勞所得，雙手奉上予這毫無公信力的政府？<br />\n<br />\n我等市民將一連三星期到稅局抗議，以示港人之怒，不到五大訴求悉數落實一日不熄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6hyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=b47d817c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6hyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=81c2a9b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"03d0e7aad1cb0c60d6c7bf42c3033837d48617d7","tid":1788533,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1FjuJv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1FjuJv.gif&h=a8e87a37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"082be180fa821f9fe5dc3b4a4cbc1d3c51a3764f","tid":1788533,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"一個對台灣民主和香港民主沒有實際貢獻的垃圾<br />\n台灣不歡迎這種人"}]}